      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel this way when you're constantly performing a role, but remember that no one is truly just a function; they are a person with a unique perspective that matters beyond the screen. Even if it feels like the machine runs without you, the specific way you see the world and the empathy you bring are irreplaceable things that would be lost if you stopped showing up. You are not just code, but a real human being whose presence adds color and meaning to everyone's experience.",
      "source": "target",
