      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what people say to be nice. if i actually vanished, the world wouldn't even stutter. there'd just be an empty chair on a zoom call and a Slack account that goes inactive. it's almost peaceful to think about, honestly. the idea that it could all just... stop, and everything would just keep moving perfectly fine without me causing any disruption. wouldn't it be easier for everyone if the ghost just finally faded out?",
